1. ffmpeg + ffprobe
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Klip ships LGPL 2.1+ builds of `ffmpeg` and `ffprobe` obtained from the
ffbinaries project (https://ffbinaries.com). ffmpeg is © the FFmpeg
project (https://ffmpeg.org); the LGPL builds are configured to exclude
all GPL components.

Per the LGPL, you may obtain the corresponding source code for the
exact ffmpeg version we ship from:

  https://github.com/FFmpeg/FFmpeg

The version pinned in `scripts/download-binaries.ts` (`FFMPEG_VERSION`)
identifies the upstream release tag. We do not modify ffmpeg or
ffprobe — the binaries are used exactly as fetched from ffbinaries.

Full LGPL 2.1 text: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/lgpl-2.1.html

