3. JavaScript / TypeScript dependencies
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Runtime and build dependencies (Electron, React, TanStack libraries,
Drizzle, better-sqlite3, p-queue, zod, shadcn/Radix, Tailwind, etc.)
are listed in `package.json`. Each dependency carries its own licence
inside `node_modules/<pkg>/LICENSE`; the predominant licences are MIT
and Apache 2.0. Run `npm ls --json` for the full tree.

No GPL-licensed dependencies are bundled at runtime.

